body_html:
Hi all -- the current einsum implementation expects the output indices to be in alphabetical order (that should be fairly straightforward to fix, though). Other than that, I think it should work correctly.

@xuancong84 Have you noticed any other bugs? Would it be easier to talk offline about any other unimplemented functionality you'd like to see?
